siddhi-gpl-execution-r.description: The siddhi-gpl-execution-r extension is an extension to Siddhi that can be used to process events with R scripts.

siddhi-gpl-execution-pmml.description: The siddhi-gpl-execution-pmml extension is an extension to Siddhi that can be used to process texts based on a PMML processing model.

siddhi-gpl-execution-geo.description: The siddhi-gpl-execution-geo extension is an extension to Siddhi that provides geo data related functionality such as checking whether a given geo coordinate is within a predefined geo-fence, etc. Following are the functions of the Geo extension.

siddhi-gpl-execution-streamingml.description: The siddhi-execution-streamingml is an extension to Siddhi that performs streaming machine learning on event streams.

siddhi-gpl-execution-nlp.description: The siddhi-gpl-execution-nlp extension is an extension to Siddhi that can be used to process natural language.
